    "The interviews provided deeper insights into these findings.",
    "Both teachers and students acknowledged the benefits of AI, particularly in terms of personalized learning and immediate feedback.",
    "A common theme among teachers was the reduced time spent on routine tasks, allowing more focus on interactive and creative teaching.",
    "However, several teachers expressed concerns about over-reliance on technology, fearing it might diminish their role in the classroom.",
    "Students appreciated the flexibility and interactivity of AI tools."
